title: 100 American poems of the twentieth century (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Harcourt, Brace & World | 1966 | Pdf | Eng | 289 pag | 34.9 MB

There are one hundred poems in this book, each followed by a commentary. No claim is made that these are the hundred best American poems of the twentieth century. Such a claim is beyond proof. What can be shown, on the other hand, is that a poem has merit and distinction, and in various ways, the commentaries are a demonstration of it
